Ep1. First Time Again 
Still reeling from the deaths of Reg and Pete, Rick and the group devise a plan to lure a massive herd of walkers away from Alexandria, but a new development puts the entire community at risk. 

Ep2. JSS 
Carol and Morgan lead a line of defense against The Wolves when Alexandria comes under attack, as Enid's past comes to light. 

Ep3. Thank You 
In a race against time, Glenn and Michonne try to lead the Alexandrians back home before the herd catches up to them. 

Ep4. Here's Not Here 
Morgan tells the Alpha Wolf about his journey from King County to Alexandria, where he met a lone survivor with a code. 

Ep5. Now 
Alexandria recovers from the Wolves' attack. Maggie and Aaron search for Glenn. Deanna questions her leadership. 

Ep6. Always Accountable 
Wounded after being separated from Abraham and Sasha, Daryl finds himself captive of three survivors on the run. 

Ep7. Heads Up 
Glenn and Enid make their way back to Alexandria. Meanwhile, Spencer puts his life a risk, as the herd finds its way inside the safe-zone. 

Ep8. Start to Finish 
With the walls down, Alexandria finds itself swarmed by walkers. Meanwhile, the tension between Carol and Morgan comes to head, as the Alpha Wolf makes his move. 

Ep9. No Way Out 
Daryl, Abraham and Sasha face-off against the Saviors. Back at Alexandria, Rick and his group make their way through the herd, as Denise finds herself at the hands of the Alpha Wolf. 

Ep10. The Next World 
Rick and Daryl cross paths with Jesus, a mysterious man with many secrets. Meanwhile, Michonne helps Spencer find closure, as Carl recovers from his injury. 

Ep11. Knots Untie 
Jesus takes Rick and the group to the Hilltop Colony, a peaceful community overshadowed by the power of Negan and The Saviors. 

Ep12. Not Tomorrow Yet 
Back from the Hilltop, Rick rallies Alexandria to a surprise attack on the Saviors' compound. Gabriel steps it up, as two group members are captured. 

Ep13. The Same Boat 
Carol and Maggie must fight for their lives after being taken by a group of Saviors. 

Ep14. Twice as Far 
After a minor victory against The Saviors, a supply run led by Daryl turns chaotic when he and his group cross paths with Dwight. 

Ep15. East 
Rick and Morgan set out in the search for Carol. Meanwhile, Daryl and Rosita track down Dwight, as Glenn and Michonne fall into a trap. 

Ep16. Last Day on Earth 
Morgan makes a sacrifice in order to save Carol. Meanwhile, Rick and the group travel to the Hilltop with an ailing Maggie, as the confrontation with Negan looms near.
